# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __rpow__, __rlshift__, __rrshift__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows.
# decimal.Decimal defines __rpow__ (true x1); __rlshift__ and __rrshift__ are
# absent from Decimal.__dict__ (false x2). All other decimal classes define none
# of the three (false x15).
# Decimal supports reflected exponentiation but not bitwise shift, which is
# an integer-only operation incompatible with IEEE 754 decimal arithmetic.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

